	(322, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Congo (RDC)', '1. Be smart and easily understand the subjects being taught in school.\r\n2. Finish school with good grades.\r\n3. Have clear goals.\r\n4. Have a career that I’ll love.\r\n5. Be successful.\r\n6. Have a rich husband who protects me no matter what.\r\n7. Have a husband that is understanding, calm, sweet, charming, charismatic,smart and God-fearing.\r\n8. Have a husband who helps me through my ups and downs with God.\r\n9. Be able to support my husband mentally and emotionally.\r\n10. Have a supportive husband for my projects.\r\n11. Be stronger mentally.\r\n12. Maintain a stable prayer life.\r\n13. Constantly stay close to the Lord.\r\n14. Make right choices.\r\n15. Be a resourceful mother and wife.\r\n16. Be a mother that my kids enjoy being with.\r\n17. Encourage and guide my kids closer to God.\r\n18. Have kids that can open up to me.\r\n19. Be open-minded to my kids’ mental, physical, and emotional needs and be there to support them.\r\n20. Have living room kids who are not scared to be around me and their dad.\r\n21. Have a huge creativity.\r\n22. Be a woman of God.\r\n23. Have peace of mind.\r\n24. Be happy.\r\n25. My parents to live a long life.\r\n26. Be able to support my parents financially.\r\n27. For Kinshasa to be a better and more developed country.', '2025-01-16 16:56:30', '2025-01-16 16:56:30'),
