	(801, 'Cristina Francisco', 'cristinafrancisco40@gmail.com', '06767776785', 'Austria', 'Schalom \r\nNa 2024 na zuaki Vision  Pendant la priere que Makila ezali kosopana na Ba gynecologue  etondi tobondela po ekatana to bondelaki kasi ti lelo \r\nBa jeune fille ekomi pasi po ba simba bana awa biso na Autriche pe na Europe ba zemi kaka kolongua balobi ezali pona tonga ya Corona oyo ba jeune ba zuaki ebebisi makila tozali na fille na biso moko pe ekomeliye esengeli Vatis lisusu ba traitement \r\nYango nasengi lisungi ya priere \r\nMerci', '2025-01-17 04:04:21', '2025-01-17 04:04:21'),
